50|$|In Malaysia, the <b>direct</b> <b>debit</b> {{system is}} {{available}} via the product known as FPX - Financial Process Exchange. FPX supports online <b>direct</b> <b>debit</b> {{as well as}} batch <b>direct</b> <b>debit.</b> It opens new doors for e-commerce in Malaysia, in particular business to business (B2B) and business to commerce (B2C) payments.|$|E
