50|$|Cashplus prepaid MasterCard’s {{and digital}} current {{accounts}} provide {{an alternative to}} traditional bank accounts in the UK. They offer a secure means to shop online and in store (worldwide, utilising the MasterCard network), make and receive payments (including <b>Direct</b> <b>Debits</b> and Standing Orders) and manage money.|$|R
5000|$|Standing {{orders are}} {{distinct}} from direct debits; both are methods {{of setting up}} repeated transfers of money from one account to another, but they operate in different ways. The fundamental difference is that standing orders send payments arranged by the payer, while <b>direct</b> <b>debits</b> are specified and collected by the payee.|$|R
